snippet.title: Trimorta Trailer v1.2
snippet.description:
Trimorta is a horror-adventure game where you explore a space fortress in search of your five missing crewmates.

v1.2 Update:
-New unlockable difficulty "Hardcore Mode."
-Various fixes, improvements & additions.

https://polysplitgames.itch.io/trimorta
